SUMMARY:CHRIS CAIN BAND
DESCRIPTION:DINNER SHOW with THE CHRIS CAIN BAND\nTake some influence from B.B. King\, Albert King\, Ray Charles\, and a pinch of Albert Collins. Add in dazzling blues and jazz guitar chops\, a rich soulful baritone vocal delivering original\, often wry and beleaguered lyrics with sophisticated chord changes and instrumentation\, and skills on various horns and keyboards\, all delivered with an uptown cool that never lacks searing passion. It all adds up to the one and only Chris Cain\, who has gone from being a newcomer phenomenon bursting onto the blues scene in 1987 with a classic debut release\, to being a legend\, inspiration and long-established member of the blues pantheon.
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/chris-cain-band-3/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ranchonicasio.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-Cain-Band.jpg
END:VEVENT
