SUMMARY:SHA NA NOW - Rancho Debut!
DESCRIPTION:DINNER SHOW WITH SHA NA NOW- Rancho Debut!\nA tribute to legendary Sha Na Na!\nSha Na Now celebrates the best of the best classic rock-n-roll music from the 50’s and 60’s. With front man Frankie Adel – former lead singer from Sha Na Na – bringing his dynamic stage presence\, this band will keep you dancing all night long.  Members’ collective experience includes working with some of music’s greats such as: Celine Dion\, Hall & Oates\, Huey Lewis\, Beach Boys\, Paul Anka\, Kenny Rogers and more.  You will be amazed to remember just how great this music from Rock’s golden age was\, and is!
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/sha-na-now-rancho-debut/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ranchonicasio.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/SHA-NA-NOW.jpg
END:VEVENT
