SUMMARY:MIRACLE MULE
DESCRIPTION:Dinner & A Show with MIRACLE MULE \nMiracle Mule is a rocking\, hoof-stomping\, tail-swishing band from Marin County\, California. Some folks might describe our music as good-time Americana\, others might say it’s down-home country with a heavy dose of Louisiana hot sauce. We prefer to just call it “swampy tonk.” However you describe it\, it’s fun and energetic\, irresistibly danceable\, with rich harmonies and solid song writing. We play at most of the more prestigious venues in the north bay\, as well as a host of wineries\, festivals and concert series. We have a loyal following\, but there’s always room for more. Check us out soon. Dance\, Laugh\, Bray.
URL:https://ranchonicasio.com/event/miracle-mule-4/
LOCATION:Rancho Nicasio\, 1 Old Rancheria Rd\, Nicasio\, CA\, 94946\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://ranchonicasio.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Miracle-Mule.jpg
END:VEVENT
